                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">伪</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">装</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">暗暗的掐了一下自己</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我还知道疼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">那就不是梦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不是幻觉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不由得心里叫起来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">怎办怎办</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可依然不想表露出来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">甚至还要装出几份冷漠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">让谁都清楚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我真的没有在意</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">其实内心却很纠结</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">只好继续伪装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">回</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">忆</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不知何故</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">总会想起你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">也许是缘份让我们邂逅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">生命中留下的痕迹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">似乎总是不能抹去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我欣赏你的年轻有为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">你爱看我写出的诗情画意</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">而你的歌声</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">也像涓涓细流</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">滋润我干涸的心田</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">从此我便锁住了你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">还记得你鼓起勇气来看我吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">那时兴奋的笑容</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">像一树盛开着的繁花</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">让我心中始终充满回忆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
