                    "title": "红柳河畔话沧桑",
                    "summary": "在榆林靖边的北端，有一条无定河支流红柳河，河的北岸是一望无际的草滩，",
                    "author": "文／王建霞",
                    "recUnit": "靖边县团委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/24.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "大美榆林",
                    "twoColumn": "地理榆林",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在榆林靖边的北端，有一条无定河支流红柳河，河的北岸是一望无际的草滩，翠绿、秀美、灵气，与印象里的沙漠、沙海有很大的反差，我的心情由一种说不清的沉重变成了另一种兴奋。这大概是榆林人几十年治沙的成果吧！大夏国赫连勃勃第一次踏上这里，就喜不自禁地发出诗人般的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;美哉，斯阜，临光泽而带清流&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">感叹。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">今天，我来这里，正是要寻访大夏国的都城遗址&mdash;&mdash;统万城。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">绿色处，统万城高大的马面醒目的跃入视线，盛夏的炎炎烈日将这座独特的白色古城照得更加苍白，与蓝天、白云、绿野四色形成一种宁静平和画面。统万城像一位时光老人，静静地眺望着那条涓涓流淌的红柳河，注视着不同的饮水人。沉默地看着一拨一拨的游人，听人们说起自己的历史，不与世争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">太阳还是那个太阳，天空还是那个天空，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年的时空，斗转星移，风云浩荡，五座墩台和连着的残垣断壁，历经岁月的打磨，变得千疮百孔，似一个古老民族伤势未愈合而留下的伤口，又似一张张失语的嘴巴，张着嘴却无法告诉人们自己的沧桑身世，让人感受到一种苍凉的况味。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">统万城，五胡十六国时期大夏国的国都，匈奴赫连勃勃的皇城。因其呈白色，当地人称之为白城子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">413</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，东晋，正是匈奴走向鼎盛的时期，匈奴王赫连勃勃和他的部下为寻一处风水宝地建国都，风尘仆仆来到了榆林靖边红柳河北岸。大将叱干阿利奉赫连勃勃之命，招募</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万民众，日夜施工七年，于公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">419</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，建成了这座白色的大夏都城。《晋书》上载有大夏国秘书监胡义所撰的《统万城铭》，其中记载：&ldquo;高隅蔽日，崇墉际云，石郭天池，周绵千里。&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;华林池沼，重台密室，通房连阁，驰道苑园。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">也许赫连勃勃修建统万城的初心是想和他的族党在这里过安定的生活，不再漂泊；也许是心由境起，权欲使然，面对硕大的都城，赫连勃勃自信得发出令后世都感到惊世骇俗的话：&ldquo;朕方统一天下，君临万邦，可以统万为名。&rdquo;于是，这座城便定名为统万城。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">统万城西城为内宫，宫殿林立，赫连勃勃给西城的东南西北四座城门分别叫&ldquo;招魏&rdquo;、&ldquo;朝宋&rdquo;、&ldquo;服凉&rdquo;、&ldquo;平朔&rdquo;；东城居官厨衙署，戒备森严；居民集市在外郭城。外郭城城墙马面密集，南墙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个，东墙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个，北墙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个，西墙</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个。居民在外郭城生活、做买卖，抬头就是高高的城垛和持刀寻视的戍兵，不知道他们是有安全感，还是如惊弓之鸟惶恐不安？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">眼前的统万城，现今南墙的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个马面遗迹尚好，西南隅墩仍然高出地面达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">多米，相当于十层楼高，白苍苍的傲然于天地间，成了今人随心所欲赏阅的一道风景。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1950</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，据考古学者取样化验鉴定，统万城城土的主要成分是石英、粘土和碳酸钙。石英即沙砾，碳酸钙是石灰（氧化钙）吸收二氧化碳而成，三者加水便称为三合土。三合土是优良的建筑材料，色白，质地坚硬，现代工程仍在使用。有文献记载：&ldquo;击之火出、其坚可以砾刀斧&rdquo;。今日得见还是坚如磐石，不知道我们现代高科技的钢筋水泥建筑物能不能立于千年不倒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">民间传说，叱干阿利监造统万城时特别认真，筑城的土，全部用蒸笼蒸过，而且掺和了粘度很大的软糜子面在一起蒸，一经打成墙，便坚如石壁。城墙因掺和了软糜子面，而成了白色。叱干阿利监工还十分森严，每筑一段墙，都要用铁钉椎之，凡椎不进去者有奖，椎进一寸，即杀工匠，然后拆掉重筑，并连人也筑进城墙内。这些传说是不是真的笔者无法考证，但小时候曾听母亲讲过，民国时期，灾荒年死了不少人，当地很多村民饿的不行，就用刀抠统万城的泥土吃。有人说是饿死的，也有人说是泥土吃进胃坠而致死。统万城是否真的掺和了软糜子面，当地人很信服，一方面因为统万城土白而且特别像软米面一样粘细，另一方面因靖边地处北疆，无霜期短，只适合种糜子、荞麦等小日月庄稼，所以靖边一带至今盛产糜子、荞麦，软黄米糕和剁荞面一直是靖边的地方传统风味。这个传说就这样似真的一样被传了下来。至于，叱干阿利监工时的残忍，在此我不作深究。这世界原本是动物的世界，待初进化到人类，不驯服者遭到杀戮还是家常便饭，人类的文明史本来就是从带有血腥味的野性史中走过来的，我们无法用今人的眼光知道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年前的人事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">赫连勃勃生于公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">381</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，本姓刘。刘姓是汉朝皇帝所赐与的。本属于匈奴铁弗部，&ldquo;铁弗匈奴&rdquo;是内迁南匈奴单于后裔的一支。&ldquo;铁弗&rdquo;是胡语，意思是&ldquo;胡父鲜卑母&rdquo;。其生逢正值各少数民族入主中原的&ldquo;五胡乱华&rdquo;时期，匈奴、氐、羌、鲜卑等少数民族纷纷在北方地域建立一个个分裂割据的政权。胜者为王败者为寇，华夏江山，谁都可以打打杀杀；谁都可以称帝为王；谁都可以到处作营盘；谁都可以建皇宫。狼多肉少，权欲让一些人变得性格古怪、诡异，即使你不攻他，他也要密谋算计着打你，你对对手仁慈，对手还是要置你于死地。因此，群王之间，如剑拔弩张，似斗红了头的公鸡，你争我夺，互不相让，每个小国就像拴在一根绳上的蚂蚱，谁也逃不脱命运的摆布，强悍的想让自己的小国强大起来，儒弱的小国想保一份平安不受欺负。于是，有的奋起反抗、有的联盟攻击、有的无奈和亲。这样的社会，但凡有志气、有野心之人，有谁会坐以待毙，有谁会甘心任人摆布，何况这些群王都是血性刚刚的汉子，自小受尽磨难的赫连勃勃自然不甘。然而，不管是出于何种原因，战争总会带给人类灾难，让人深感悲哀。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">刘勃勃的父亲刘卫辰是匈奴铁弗部族的首领，公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">390</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，在征战中被北魏击败身亡。北魏诛杀刘卫辰宗党五千多人，并将尸体全部扔进黄河。年仅十岁的刘勃勃单骑逃亡投奔鲜卑叱干部首领。叱干部首领畏惧北魏，欲将勃勃交给北魏。送往途中，叱干部首领的侄子劫走刘勃勃，并将其送到后秦高平公那里。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">刘勃勃仪表堂堂，才能出众，高平公先是把女儿嫁给刘勃勃，后又引荐给后秦郡主姚兴。姚兴是位爱才之人，他认为刘勃勃有济世之才，重用刘勃勃为安远将军，镇守朔方，领辖今宁夏自治区盐池与榆林定边一带。后来，姚兴与北魏通好，家仇国恨，勃勃大怒，与后秦反目，拥兵自立。后秦郡主十分动怒，曾数次征讨，公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">409</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，在今延安黄陵西北进行的二城之战，刘勃勃均得胜。赫连勃勃认为匈奴是夏后氏之苗裔，便于东晋义熙三年（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">407</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）年，自称大夏天王，大单于，在今之靖边建立夏国，建号&ldquo;大夏&rdquo;，从此，大夏国成为了十六国之一。公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">413</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，刘勃勃废除刘姓，改姓赫连氏，寓意为自己是天之骄子，自己的显赫是天命。从此，刘勃勃变成了赫连勃勃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">事实证明，每一位干事业、或成功之人都有他不同于别人或过人之处。赫连勃勃确实是一位非凡之人，不管他在历史上扮演了什么角色，他选国都榆林，就表现出了他聪明的军事才能。榆林南靠中原汉中地区的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">800</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">里秦川，有富足的粮食，北临内蒙古大草原，有广余的牧草，因此，占据了榆林，就等于有了人畜无后顾之忧的仓库。榆林这块土地自商周以来，战乱年代一直是兵家的必争之地，使当地百姓生灵涂炭，原来水草丰美的地方经历历代的蹂躏后土地逐渐沙化，当然，这是后话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">赫连勃勃于乱国中在榆林靖边建国都，统万城逐渐走向强盛时期。赫连勃勃本可以固守这里，兴国安邦，让自己的子民安居乐业。但或许是欲望所使，或许是有&ldquo;逼上梁山&rdquo;的隐衷，他驱动&ldquo;铁弗&rdquo;骑兵，驰骋北国，东征西讨，先后夺取南凉、后秦等诸国大批土地和人口、牲畜，&ldquo;岭北夷夏降附者数十万&rdquo;，公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">416</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，夺下长安，占据了秦岭以北的大片地域。据《读史方舆纪要》卷三载：勃勃盛时，南阻秦岭，东戍蒲津，西收秦陇，北薄于河。疆域包括今陕西秦岭以北，内蒙古河套地区，山西太原、临汾西南部及甘肃东南部，成为北方的一大强国。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">赫连勃勃在位</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">19</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，于公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">425</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年因病去世，时年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">45</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">岁。赫连勃勃去世后，其三公子发生内讧，被北魏太武帝拓跋焘乘机征服，公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">428</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，统万城被攻破。北魏将统万城改名为统万镇，统万城成为北魏的牧马场，养马</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">200</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">多万匹，骆驼百万余头。隋代，统万城被地方豪强梁师都割据统万城约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年；宋代，又成为党项人李继迁、李元昊等在这里称王割地的金汤之地。鉴于此，公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">994</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年，北宋为此下令拆毁统万城，将城内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">万人口迁移榆林一带，匈奴人隐名改姓融入了汉人。榆林地域很多人都有少数民族的血统，当地民间传说，现在很多刘姓就是匈奴后裔。《宋史》卷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">334</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">《徐禧传》等记载，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">800</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年后，西夏占据统万城，修复了原城，一直延用至西夏末年（约公元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1227</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年），统万城逐渐被沙漠侵袭，沦为废墟。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不知谁说过，时代造英雄，英雄造时代。不管是英雄也罢，懦夫也罢；不管是成功也罢，失败也罢；不管是慈善也罢，凶残也罢，每个时代、每个人都有每个人的活法和做法的原因。我们姑且不说赫连勃勃的功过是非，我们没有生活在那个年代，无权评判古人，特定的环境中有特定性格的人，我们可以从这个角度来理解一个人。我们也可以学习一个人的闪光点，忽视一个人的不足之处。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一座城能历经风雨，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年后傲然不到，想必我们应该无语了。喝酒的人常有一句自嘲的话，说：&ldquo;人是好人，只是酒是坏东西。&rdquo;这里我也想借用一下，赫连勃勃，人是好人，只是乱世是坏东西。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
