                    "title": "嵌在黄土沟壑上的凤凰城古堡",
                    "summary": "双锁山，古时称为双山堡，又曰凤凰城。",
                    "author": "文／陈宝生",
                    "recUnit": "榆阳区团委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/25.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "大美榆林",
                    "twoColumn": "地理榆林",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">双锁山，古时称为双山堡，又曰凤凰城。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">榆林的明长城在这儿像一条若断若续的游龙，横卧在榆关要塞的沙漠上。双山堡、建安堡、常乐堡、保宁堡、归德堡等几个古堡像它的利爪深深抓扣在黄土塬和大沙漠接壤处。双山堡就是它的一个龙爪，但从空中鸟瞰其形像一只凤凰展翅飞翔，人们又送了它一个美丽的名字&ldquo;凤凰堡&rdquo;。由于其城堡建在陡峭的黄土峁上，进进出出十分费力，但它却是西口路上的商旅栈口。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">凤凰城古堡位于榆阳区麻黄梁镇双锁山村，在榆林东南</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">80</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">里处，为明代延绥镇长城沿线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">36</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">营堡之一，属于中路榆林道管理的营堡。据道光年《榆林府志》记载：&ldquo;明正统间筑水地寨，成化时余子俊移筑今堡，并柳树会兵守之。&rdquo;堡内有楼铺</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">座，东北深沟巨壑，南面峻坡陡峭，设东西南三门，系极冲之地。万历六年（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1578</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年）重修，边垣长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">里有奇，墩台</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">座，屯驻军丁及守瞭军</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">660</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名，配马骡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">331</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">匹，设操守、坐堡、守备等军丁。到清康熙年屯驻守兵</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">100</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">名，设守备统辖。那些高高低低的古窑老门，隐藏着多少秘密，才能支撑起凤凰城小街的门面。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">沧桑变迁，几经战火。凤凰城的祖先一代一代繁衍，一代又一代扎下根来，古堡居民晴耕雨读，建设自己的家园&hellip;&hellip;五百年弹指一挥间，安与乱、富与贫、荣与衰、乐与痛，早已烟消云散，只留下一座断壁残垣的古城墙，一个古堡的废墟骷髅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">依稀还记得，那个初春的早晨，阳光灿烂，小街遇集，小商小贩拥挤在小街上，有些是来自高家堡和碎金镇的商旅。由于其地理环境特殊，得天独厚的红白两家秘密交易市场的存在，车马店里拴着不少的马帮和驼队，一股燥热的臭气，熏人欲倒。凤凰城古堡小村看上去生机勃勃，村旁屹立着一座古寺，香烟缭绕。绿色的嫩草刚刚露头，一个放牧人躺在小沙坡上，静悠悠地看着自己的羊儿，嘴里衔着笛子不时吹出陕北特有的&ldquo;爬山调&rdquo;。逛够了小街，绕过一道山梁，登上集市后的小土岗，双目被那逶迤的黄土浪谷、风动无垠的丘陵冲沟占满，被那似曾熟悉的典型环境所吸引，心潮随着苍茫古韵的地貌激动起伏&mdash;&mdash;这是我</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1958</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年首次来到凤凰城所看到的瞬间风貌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">当我看到了这块群峰涌浪、云气氤氲的灵山地域，才把疲惫、麻木的心情安顿下来。这块山有灵气、峰有灵感的陕北黄土典型地貌，顿觉使我的创作得到提升，不由自主地心随山引、景遂目移，寻觅到最佳的拍摄位置和最佳的画面。在快门定格后我哼出一首小诗：黑夜流星魂一幕，高原红日光一束，艺术师法不宜法，搜尽群峰有倾吐。影生风雷燃火炬，图耀斑斓书沉浮，功深百炼艺生辉，生命图像大彻悟。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为了展示全景式俯视画面，我便登高远眺，以散点视角取势佳构，那神工鬼斧、匠心无痕，那苍秀粗犷、峻拔伟岸的黄土山势，仿佛就是你要寻找的支撑你的理想图景。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">突然间山坳里鞭炮齐鸣，一阵阵喜庆的锣鼓传来，此起彼伏。原来这天是一个良辰吉日，一行披红挂彩骑着毛驴的娶亲队伍走来，为黄土沟壑增添了喜庆热烈的气氛。骑在毛驴上的新娘羞涩面庞像三月桃花绽放开来，陶醉在黄漫漫的古道上。静静山峁蓦然红火起来，创作激情驱使下迅速登上山巅，啊，太美了！连绵的丘壑，云遮雾罩；红色的梁峁，姹紫嫣红；一幅红妆素裹、分外妖娆的景象顿使你心花怒放，激情澎湃！我想这一幅《云横双锁山，山乡红烂漫》的画面，也许是受了北宋张泽端《清明上河图》的影响，所展现边塞这一方水土中的百姓怡然自若的生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抬头仰望，浩瀚的黄土丘壑绵亘在天地间，雷鞭电击锻造出来山势肌理，雨塑风雕冲刷出来的血脉沟纹，将埋藏在心底的佳构唤醒。站在山峁上仿佛是在大鹏背上鸟瞰，身感风动的梁峁犹似万象奔驰&hellip;&hellip;平远、深远、高远的景象融为一图：褶皱里的窑院，悬崖上的人家，湖面上的小舟，沙坡上的农夫，是一种生命力的亢奋、狂放，一种时代风采精神的旋律。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">双山堡&mdash;&mdash;一个酷似展翅的金凤凰，飞翔在榆关要塞的绝壁凌空。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">嵌在黄土沟壑崖壁上的凤凰城古堡，人们慢悠悠的生活节奏，是凤凰城的主旋律。那崖壁上的古村，黄土窑院里的人家，阳光从晨起到夕晖的照耀，像扫描一样在梁峁上移动，洒下明亮温暖的光芒，像一个熟睡的美人梳理着独特的腰肢。无论是在汉朝还是宋朝，无论是在明清还是当今社会，对于中国西部的凤凰城古堡来说，沧海桑田，岁月变迁，无非是在这块亘古地域上增添几道道血脉沟纹，增添了一些群说纷纭的古堡注释，也给人们留下了一些神秘遗韵。凤凰城不同凡响丘陵山壑，不同式样的血脉丹青，在今天申报黄土地质公园，开发性的旅游热潮中，却能玉成其美。摄影家、画家、电影家和广大发烧友们等观光者，能仰而望峰、俯而观湖，遥对黄土画面，目送水痕丹青，游目骋怀，意犹未尽。阅尽这一片榆林乃至西部不多见的峰峦山势凤凰城古堡，也许能成就榆林旅游事业一隅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/25.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
