                    "firstColumn": "大美榆林",
                    "twoColumn": "舌尖上的榆林",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">前些时日，榆林城不知不觉中出现了许多牛杂汤饭馆。从西沙到东沙，从北门到南门，随处可见。也许是榆林人羊杂汤喝腻了，又开始喝牛杂汤了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这不，我们一帮老同学无意中找到榆林西二路&ldquo;乡二郎牛杂味道&rdquo;品汤叙旧。其装潢颇有些讲究，门面是普通砖瓦式的，墙面是泥土麦草抹就的，而那些农耕用具和饸饹床子便有了一些庄户人家的气息，难怪其门面上贴的对联是：乡二郎的牛杂汤，庄户人的好味道。大众口味，这大概就是其看家护院的拿手戏吧。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">牛杂汤有一个美丽的传说：上古一位大王看到天旱地荒，老百姓饥不择食，便在先农坛祭祀祈雨，这份爱心感动了老天爷，天降大雨。大王当即下令将所养的牛都屠宰了，把牛的肚、心、肝、肠等放入锅中煮熟，其味道鲜美，营养丰富，被称之为&ldquo;牛杂碎&rdquo;。而后，历代牛杂的选料主要是牛肚、牛肠、牛肺等，俗称&ldquo;牛肉串&rdquo;。而乡二郎牛杂汤精选鲜品牛杂，采用传统工艺，用牛杂煮</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">制出白色的杂汤，再将牛杂充分煮熟，经现代加工技术生产出牛杂汤包及调料包等，食用时将牛杂放入锅内烧开，再加入调料包充分调匀，其色泽醒目，鲜香可口，百食不厌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>",
                    "magaThumburl": "/magazine/userfiles/_thumbs/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/08/29.jpg,",
                    "count": "",
