                    "title": "清涧煎饼",
                    "summary": "清涧煎饼是陕西省榆林市清涧县一种独特的汉族风味小吃。",
                    "author": "",
                    "recUnit": "清涧县团委",
                    "contact": "",
                    "relDate": "2016-08-31",
                    "magaImgurl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/11/30.jpg",
                    "magaLogourl": "|/magazine/userfiles/files/mag/mgMagazine/2016/10/aaa(1).jpg",
                    "firstColumn": "大美榆林",
                    "twoColumn": "舌尖上的榆林",
                    "periodicalDate": "2016-08",
                    "state": "",
                    "periodical": "103",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">清涧煎饼是陕西省榆林市清涧县一种独特的汉族风味小吃。煎饼状若朗夜之圆月，晶莹如白雪，轻薄似蝉翼，柔韧绵冽，其味沁人心肺，过口难忘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">制作清涧煎饼的原材料是荞麦。荞麦富含钙、铁、磷、锌以及赖氨酸等营养元素。早在元代王桢《农中》就有荞麦&ldquo;治去皮壳，磨而成面，摊作煎饼，配蒜而食&rdquo;的记载，可谓历史悠久了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">清涧煎饼的制作工艺非常讲究。先要将荞麦粗磨去皮，得了糁子，再将糁子用水浸足，再将多余的水倒出，浸透的糁子装罗布做的袋子中反复揉搓，挤出浆液，按一定的比例兑水后，再用特制的煎饼鏊摊制成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">厘米大的如纸薄饼，可以卷绿豆芽或黑豆芽加粉丝、肉丝、炸豆腐丝凉拌，或卤猪头肉、猪肘子等其他卤肉剁碎加适量青椒和蒜粒，蘸煎饼汤（姜蒜汤汁）或熬制的番茄酱汁就可以吃了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<!--EndFragment-->150%;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&#39;&gt;制出白色的杂汤，再将牛杂充分煮熟，经现代加工技术生产出牛杂汤包及调料包等，食用时将牛杂放入锅内烧开，再加入调料包充分调匀，其色泽醒目，鲜香可口，百食不厌。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
